<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.2.4">
<l>maṟaṅko ḷāḷari yuruveṉa veruvara voruvaṉa takalmārvam</l>
<l>tiṟantu vāṉavar maṇimuṭi paṇitara viruntanal limayattuḷ</l>
<l>iṟaṅki yēṉaṅkaḷ vaḷaimarup piṭantiṭak kiṭantaru kerivīcum</l>
<l>piṟaṅku māmaṇi yaruviyo ṭiḻitaru piriticeṉ ṟaṭaiṉeñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In the fair Himalayas where [he] resides, as celestials bow</l>
<l rend="indent">their jewel-crowned [heads],</l>
<l>Having split open that one’s broad chest to cause fear</l>
<l rend="indent">in the form of a vicious man-lion,</l>
<l>[My] heart, go and take refuge at Piriti where glistening huge jewels</l>
<l rend="indent">naturally descend with cascades</l>
<l>Which, landing nearby, emit fire as boars, bending down, dig [them] up</l>
<l rend="indent">with their curved tusks.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
